\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Eventually, however, the Alliance would secure an alliance with the Llorrai,
 offering safe asylum for refugees and full support for an independent Llorrai
 state in exchange for first trading rights to Paradise's rare mineral reserves.
 Through this treaty, the Llorrai became a valuable ally in the ongoing
 battle, and Llorrai hunters even found their way into service elsewhere
 in the Alliance military and even the Surveyor's Guild.
\end_layout

