In appearance, the Llorrai resemble many other capyfolk species found across
 the galaxy.
 Bearing a squarish head with long muzzle, prominent incisors, thick fur,
 and slightly-webbed hands and feet, the stocky 4-foot capyfolk do indeed
 strongly resemble their Earth rodent counterpart.
 They are naturally quick on their feet, excellent swimmers, and Llorrai
 hunters are masters of stealth and wilderness survival.
 Unlike their Earth counterpart, the Llorrai have adapted to an omnivorous
 diet and a knack for scavenging more similar to that of rats, allowing
