\begin_layout Standard
Of course, while S.T.E.V.E.
 was one of the first and still most popular intelligent robots in service
 across the galaxy, since its release there has been an sizeable boom in
 the market.
 The success of CMCC's new android lead to a wave of other robotics and
 cybernetics manufacturers rushing their own intelligent robots to market,
 with widely varying results.
 While S.T.E.V.E.
