 CHA checks.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
Anti-Grav
\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset

Lifts Rather than ordinary physical limbs to provide motility, the robot
 has a set of anti-gravity hover lifts which bear it aloft.
 Under normal operation the robot hovers approximantly 1.5 to 2 feet above
 the ground, but may elevate in short bursts to essentially 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

jump
\begin_inset Quotes erd
